_competitor/
top_notebooks/

# Archived pre-academic-refocus snapshot (heavy run artefacts; see archief2/README.md)
archief2/

# Logs (data is captured in summary.json files)
logs/
*.log

# OS / IDE artefacts
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# Claude Code metadata (per-machine state, not source)
.claude/
